data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Wow, you will love the location of this townhome overlooking a pond and preserve.  One of the best locations in the community. No rear neighbors and you can enjoy nature from your screened porch.  Enter the home into a welcoming foyer. The door to the garage is on the left and a half bathroom is on the right. You will love the convenience of the open kitchen with an island with granite tops and an upgraded quartz double sink. The kitchen counters are granite and the cabinets have new door pulls. The interior was recently painted with Sherwin William Paint. Additional ceiling fans have been added, including the screened porch. A whole-house water softener is included. The laundry room is conveniently located on the 2nd floor near the bedrooms. Your primary bedroom has an ensuite bathroom and two closets. Very neat and clean and move-in ready. The low quarterly fee includes grounds maintenance, trash pickup, and community amenities which include 2 pools, a clubhouse with a fitness center, a basketball court, a playground with equipment, a dog park, two sports fields, and access to the Suncoast Trail. A shopping center is located at the entrance to the community and you are just minutes from the Suncoast Parkway with easy access to Tampa International Airport, and downtown Tampa. The popular Wiregrass Mall and Tampa Premium Outlets are a short drive away.
